annotationA: Lethal (3) 02640; Hydroxymethylbilane synthase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: peptidyl-pyrromethane cofactor linkage; tetrapyrrole biosynthetic process
annotationB: Uroporphyrinogen decarboxylase; Catalyzes the decarboxylation of four acetate groups of uroporphyrinogen-III to yield coproporphyrinogen-III
